21\/refuge-harm-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":23591,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from harming another Muslim","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 21, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Rashid reported: I came to Abdullah ibn Amr, and I said, \u201cNarrate to me what you have heard from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Abdullah set out a scroll, and he said, \u201cThis is what the Messenger of Allah has written for me.\u201d I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35276,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/20\/special-place-jahannam\/","url_meta":{"origin":23591,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ostentation: Special place in Hell for reciters showing off","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeek refuge in Allah from the pit of sorrow.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the pit of sorrow?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt is a valley in Hell from which Hell itself seeks refuge\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/23591","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-js